Third Department,

April, 1986

(April 1, 1986) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Jorge Briones, Petitioner, v John R. O’Keefe, as Superintendent of the Ogdensburg Correctional Facility, Respondent.

— Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (b) (2), for writ of habeas corpus denied. Kane, J. P., Mikoll, Yesawich, Jr., Levine and Harvey, JJ., concur.
